      &lt;h2 class=&quot;my-0 mb-[16px] text-ellipsis text-[18px] font-medium text-emphasis&quot;&gt;
        延伸阅读
      &lt;/h2&gt;
      
          &lt;a referrer=&quot;null&quot; href=&quot;https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/story20250221-5910434&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot; class=&quot;title&quot; id=&quot;mobile-recommend-articles&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;my-0 line-clamp-4 leading-normal&quot;&gt;
              下午察：李彦宏的缺席与百度掉队
            &lt;/div&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;relative min-w-[120px] w-[120px]&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;img alt=&quot;下午察：李彦宏的缺席与百度掉队&quot; title=&quot;下午察：李彦宏的缺席与百度掉队&quot; src=&quot;https://cassette.sphdigital.com.sg/image/zaobao/2396da6bcc8955061c58d12e976582c5e7fee6023a52b5d7cd447518d91a4803&quot; class=&quot;my-0 w-full rounded-[4px] object-contain&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;
